Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.50,0:17:17.73,SONG EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\blur2}Another sky, a different path
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.66,0:17:29.56,SONG EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\blur2}You just stayed and I keep calling you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.96,0:17:43.53,SONG EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\blur2}The train will stop and I may drop
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.91,0:17:53.98,SONG EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\blur2}Just counting days, counting heart beats
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.82,0:18:03.64,SONG EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\blur2}Before the last day of the world comes
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.14,0:18:13.03,SONG EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\blur2}I need to see your smile
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.74,0:18:26.80,SONG EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\blur2}Another sky, before my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.50,0:18:34.80,SONG EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\blur2}Just like we saw together then
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.14,0:18:44.01,SONG EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\blur2}Like petals tumbling down
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.91,0:18:53.39,SONG EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\blur2}Like shadow running cross the open field
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.39,0:19:02.46,SONG EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\blur2}I can feel my pain in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.53,0:19:19.01,SONG EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\blur2}Another sky, a different path
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.36,0:19:30.12,SONG EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\blur2}Wish I could be with you
